                            <div class="comment-top mt-5 row">
                            <div class="col-lg-5 comment-bottom w3pvt_mail_grid-img">
                            <img class="img-fluid" src="images/medi.jpg" alt="">
                            </div>
                             <div class="col-lg-7 comment-bottom w3pvt_mail_grid_right">
                            <p>Bachelor of Unani Medicine & Surgery is a 5 year course. Eligibility for the course is 10+2, intermediate cleared. Admissions for such course are on the basis of counselling after clearing entrance tests depending on the colleges.In this professional course the students are taught about Regimental therapy (llaj -bit- Tadbeer), Venesection, Cupping, Diaphoresis, Diuresis, Turkish bath, Massage, Cauterization, Purging, Emesis, Exercise, Leeching, Pharmacotherapy (llaj-bit-Dawa), Dietotherapy (llaj-bit-Ghiza), Surgery (Jarahat), etc.BUMS (Bachelor of Unani Medicine and Surgery), like all alternative medical undergraduate programs that fall into the AYUSH category - Ayurveda, Yoga & Naturopathy, Unani, Siddha, and Homeopathy, is monitored by the Central Council of Indian Medicine.Unani is the system of alternative medicines. This is similar to the Ayurveda in term of the four elements and as popular as the Ayurveda.The clinical features as the sign, symptoms, laboratory features and mijaz are important to diagnose any disease.</p>
                            </div>
